About translation files, read
http://developer.skolelinux.no/info/studentgrupper/2006-hig-daisyplayer/project_management/reports/project/project.pdf
http://torafugu.com/Trolltech/qt-4.0.0/html/qtranslator.html#details

Enter newly desired translation.ts files in Gebabbel.pro in the root directory
Run lupdate Gebabbel.pro in the root directory to update the ts files
Run lrelease Gebabbel.pro in the root directory to create the qm files
